4 inhibitors.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73512/', '', 'Pegloticase, Febuxostat, Rasburicase, Probenecid, Allopurinol', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Methylphenobarbital, Phenytoin, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, More', 1767369485);
