nt CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73541/', '', 'Caspofungin, Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', 'Pegloticase, Febuxostat, Rasburicase, Probenecid', 1767369485);
